\begin_layout Standard
A number of bait-specific primers need to be designed for each e4C library:
 an extension primer, a first round PCR primer with an overhanging tail
 consisting of half the Illumina Paired End Adapter 1.0 (
\begin_inset CommandInset nomenclature
